com.almasb.fxgl.physics

Class CollisionHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.almasb.fxgl.physics.CollisionHandler

  • public abstract class CollisionHandler
extends Object
    Handler for a collision that occurred between two entities. Subclasses should override only those callbacks they are interested in.
    Author:
    Almas Baimagambetov (AlmasB) (almaslvl@gmail.com)
